{
  "stem": "2118.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now it came to-- it came to-- before March, something like February or something, the Germans started acting nice to us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- they-- some even offered to hide us-- you know, to not ask, but here and there, a person they kind of kept close to.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A close friend of mine, he was offered that he's gonna hide him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he had to get out of the camp on his own, which was no big thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You could get away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You were middle of Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was no place you could go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was guards all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The-- you have no kind of papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You had dirty clothes, all that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "By that time, it was all worn up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Oh, you have the clothes with the-- with the stripes or you have clothes with-- with the civilian clothes, they put a [INAUDIBLE] on the back, a big patch.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So nobody went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and the mayor came down from the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said he doesn't want the Jews because he's afraid they're gonna burn down the town and kill the people when-- when the Americans come.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they-- and they-- they the Germans said that the Americans are already in-- in-- Cologne, [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Keln. ?] I remember the-- the foreman my-- used to say, I'll be glad when they get to here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "At least I'll have a cigarette to smoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You know, the Americans have plenty of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They weren't afraid of the Americans coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They kind of-- they-- they wanted it, in a way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So to make it short, they-- they said we have to go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So on the beginning-- no, had to be on the end of March.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They took us out, and they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we marched out.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
